snippet.description:
New Song 2025 | Betaab Dil | Emraan Hashmi | Yami Gautam | New Hindi Song | Romantic Song | Hindi Song | Hindi New Song | New Hindi Songs | New Romantic Song | New Hindi Song 2025 | Emraan Hashmi New Song | Emraan Hashmi Songs | Yami Gautam New Song | Yami Gautam Songs | Emraan Hashmi and Yami Gautam | Romantic Song Hindi | Hindi Song 2025 | New Song | Love Song | Official  

#NewSong2025 #NewHindiSong #RomanticSong #EmraanHashmi #YamiGautam #EmraanYami #HindiSong #HindiNewSong #NewRomanticSong #NewHindiSong2025 #EmraanHashmiNewSong #YamiGautamNewSong #RomanticSongHindi #HindiSong2025 #BetaabDil #SaritDutta

‚ÄúBetaab Dil‚Äù is a heart-touching romantic Hindi song that brings back the golden era of 90s Bollywood music. Sung and composed by Sarit Dutta, this soulful melody beautifully captures the emotions of love, longing, and separation. The heartfelt lyrics by Dr. Uma Naveen Mehta paint a timeless picture of a betaab (restless) heart waiting for its beloved.

If you miss the charm of classic love songs, ‚ÄúBetaab Dil‚Äù will take you straight back to that nostalgic era of melody and emotion.

üéß Experience ‚ÄúBetaab Dil‚Äù ‚Äî A Pure Hindi Romantic Love Song
Close your eyes, feel the rhythm, and let this song remind you of the beautiful simplicity of true love. Perfect for anyone who believes in eternal romance and misses the soulful tunes of the 90s

üëâ Don‚Äôt forget to LIKE, SHARE & SUBSCRIBE for more soulful music.

Subscribe : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWj7oD9SuDcGciiBQT9BQuw?sub_confirmation=1
__________________________________________________

Song Credits
Song : Betaab Dil
Singer : Sarit Dutta
Music Composer : Sarit Dutta
Lyrics : Dr Uma Naveen Mehta
Backing Vocals : Subhajit Das
Music Produced, Mixed & Mastered by Sarit Dutta @ Rivertone Studio
__________________________________________________

Lyrics:-

Hum chahe itna hi 
Ab tera saath ho
Kya tune kabhi ye jana
Kitna dard hai mujhko

Bekhudi mein chal pade hai
Khudko hi ab mitane
Mere kadam rukte nahi 
Teri galiyon me aane se

Deewangi ki had se jyada
Hum karte hai ye pyaar tumko
Ankhon mein teri yaadein wo leke
Betaab dil chahe tujhko

Baaton ne teri
Mujhko saari raat jagaya
Sanson ne teri
Mujhko yu apna banaya

Koi lamha nahi hai mera
Jisme tu nazar na aaya
Na hamne koi khata ki
fir kyu tune di hai saja

Deewangi ki had se jyada
Hum karte hai ye pyaar tumko
Ankhon mein teri yaadein wo leke
Betaab dil chahe tujhko
_____________________________________

The road to the Chennai Esports Global Championship 2025 heats up! Witness India‚Äôs finest BGMI squads battle it out in the Semi-Finals, fighting for just a few coveted spots at the Grand LAN Finals in Chennai, India ‚Äî happening November 14 - 16, 2025.

This is where champions are forged ‚Äî every drop, rotation, and clutch matters. With ‚Çπ 50 lakh on the line and the pride of representing the region on LAN, only the best will survive the storm.

Welcome to CEGC 2025 BGMI Semi Finals

Today's Schedule:
Map 1 - ERANGEL (Group AxB)
Map 2 - MIRAMAR (Group AxC)
Map 3 - ERANGEL (Group AxB)
Map 4 - RONDO (Group BxC)
Map 5 - ERANGEL (Group BxC)

snippet.title: ek≈ç - Malayalam Movie| Official Teaser| Sandeep Pradeep|Dinjith Ayyathan| Mujeeb Majeed|Bahul Ramesh
snippet.description:
Presenting the official teaser of ek≈ç, directed by Dinjith Ayyathan, following his acclaimed film Kishkindha Kaandam. Written by Bahul Ramesh, ek≈ç marks the final chapter of his Animal Trilogy after Kishkindha Kaandam and Kerala Crime Files: Season 2, forming a collection of three standalone stories sharing a spiritual essence ‚Äî exploring crimes and moral conflicts in a world where animal presence plays a stimulating role. 

The film also marks the maiden production venture of Mr. MRK Jhayaram under his banner Aaradyaa Studios.

Directed by : Dinjith Ayyathan 
Produced by: MRK Jhayaram
Story, Screenplay, Dialogues & DOP : Bahul Ramesh  
Music : Mujeeb Majeed 
Editor : Sooraj E S
Art Director : Sajeesh Thamarassery
Production Controller : Shafi Chemmad
Audiography : Vishnu Govind 
Make Up: Rasheed Ahammed 
Costume Design: Sujith Sudhakaran 
Project Designer : Sandeep Sasidharan
DI : Color Planet Studios
Colourist : Srik Varier
Teaser Cut : Mahesh Bhuvanend
Score Premix : Balu Thankachan at 20dB Black, Chennai
Chief Associate Director : Sagar
VFX : IVFX
Stills: Rinson M B 
Marketing & Designs : Yellowtooths
Subtitles : Vivek Renjit (Break Borders) 
PRO : A S Dinesh, Vyshak C Vadakkeveed, Jinu Anilkumar
Cast : Sandeep Pradeep, Vineeth, Narain, Binu Pappu, Ashokan, Biana Momin, Sim Zhi Fei, NG Hung Shen, Ranjith Shekhar, Saheer Muhammed
Label : Muzik247

snippet.title: FINALLY ESCAPING THE PRISON LIKE A PRO | Prison Escape Simulator
snippet.description:

Song: Bajido
Singer: Gopal Bharwad, Manisha Bharwad
Artists: Chhaya Thakor, Kuldeep Mishra, Raj Chaudhary
Music: Jackie Gajjar

Ho Pataliyo Parono, Pampan Premalo
Baliyo Ne Eto Bajigariyo
Bajido Mane Valo Ne Vat Valo

Ho Tu Hale Utavali, Dharati Dhrujavati
Babbe Bedaliye Bharati Pani
Tari Hare Mari Prityu Bandhani

Ho Bajido Maro Rudo Rupalo, Nasibe Mane Maliyo

Bhave Bhav Reshu Aapane Bhela

Ho Simade Setar, Zape Chhe Zupada
Ghadu Tara Ghar Na Rotala
Jojo Re Prem Tame Ochho Na Karata
Manigar Man Na Morala

Ho Me To Jodya Hatida Bapor Tana
Lai Aavo Bhat Panida
Ek Bhana Ma Jamashu Aapane Mithuda Bhojaniya

Ho Boli Mobhare Chibari, Aadi Utari Mindaradi
Vayaro Veri Evo Vayo, Apshukan Ni Aendhani

Ho Mand Me Joya Sukh Na Shamana
Tya Dukh Na Dungare Gherya
Man Thi Manya Ene Mari Nakhya

Ho Mara Bajida Ne Have Kon Hamjave


Ho Aankhe Joyelu Kane Padelu
Hotu Nathi Badhu Hachu Re
Bajida Tamane Bhavatu Bhanu
Aaje Aam Kem Thelyu Re

Ho Bharoha Na Bhare Prityu Bandhi
Ganthyu Bandhi Hati Prem Ni
Vachano Bhuli Gai Bhela Revana
Tare Majburi Hati Kem Ni

Ho Ek Ek Shwash Maro Tara Nam No Ur Ma Me To Bharyo

Ho Khota Re Vem Ma, Bhav Maro Balyo
Haiye Thi Hu To Have Hari Gayo
Aa Bajido Kalaje Kakali Ne Royo

snippet.description:

Chess.com offer:
World Cup Offer: Get 1 month of Chess.com Premium free by clicking on the link below:
https://go.chess.com/chessbaseindia

The FIDE World Cup 2025 will take place in Goa, India from 1st to 27th of November 2025 and will witness some of the best players in action. The total prize fund of the event is US$2 million with the winner taking home US$1,20,000. There are 3 spots to the Candidates as well at stake.

Format: 
It is a 206-player knockout event. In the first round top 50 seeds get a bye. So it starts with 156 players and comes down to 78 and then the top 50 players join to have 128 players in round 2. There are 2 classical games in each match (90 mins for 40 moves + 30 mins for remaining moves with 30 seconds increment from move 1) and if the score stands at 1-1 then we have the following tiebreaks - 2 games of 15+10, 2 games of 10+10, 2 games of 5+3, 2 games of 3+2, followed by a sudden death which has a time control of 4+2 with special bidding for Black.

Schedule:
Round 1: 1st to 3rd November
Round 2: 4th to 6th November
Round 3: 7th to 9th November
Round 4: 11th to 13th November
Round 5: 14th to 16th November
Round 6: 17th to 19th November
Round 7: 21st to 23rd November
Round 8: 24th to 26th November
Each day the games start at 3 p.m. IST

Commentators:
The commentary panel consists of IM Tania Sachdev, IM Sagar Shah, Amruta Mokal, GM Harshit Raja, GM Sahaj Grover and Sahil Tickoo.

Get the tickets: https://in.bookmyshow.com/sports/fide-world-cup-2025/ET00468629
Pairings: https://worldcup2025.fide.com/tournament-bracket/

snippet.title: Kerala Blasters FC 3-0 Sporting Club Delhi | AIFF Super Cup 2025-26 | Group D | Highlights
snippet.description:
Kerala Blasters FC produced a dominant display to thrash Sporting Club Delhi 3-0 in their second AIFF Super Cup 2025-26 Group D fixture at the GMC Stadium in Bambolim on Monday, November 3, 2025. All the goals came in the first half.

A brace from Koldo Obieta (17‚Äô, 22‚Äô) and Korou Singh‚Äôs acrobatic strike (34‚Äô) sealed a comfortable victory for the Blasters, who now sit top of the group with six points from two matches. The result also confirmed SC Delhi‚Äôs elimination from the tournament, while Kerala Blasters strengthened their bid for a semi-final berth.

id.title: Kerala Blasters FC 3-0 Sporting Club Delhi | Piala Super AIFF 2025-26 | Grup D | Cuplikan
id.description:
Kerala Blasters FC tampil dominan dengan mengalahkan Sporting Club Delhi 3-0 dalam pertandingan kedua Grup D Piala Super AIFF 2025-26 di Stadion GMC, Bambolim, pada Senin, 3 November 2025. Semua gol tercipta di babak pertama.

Dua gol dari Koldo Obieta (17', 22') dan tendangan akrobatik Korou Singh (34') memastikan kemenangan mudah bagi Blasters, yang kini memuncaki grup dengan enam poin dari dua pertandingan. Hasil ini juga memastikan tersingkirnya SC Delhi dari turnamen, sementara Kerala Blasters memperkuat asa mereka untuk lolos ke semifinal.

en.title: Kerala Blasters FC 3-0 Sporting Club Delhi | AIFF Super Cup 2025-26 | Group D | Highlights
en.description:
Kerala Blasters FC produced a dominant display to thrash Sporting Club Delhi 3-0 in their second AIFF Super Cup 2025-26 Group D fixture at the GMC Stadium in Bambolim on Monday, November 3, 2025. All the goals came in the first half.

A brace from Koldo Obieta (17‚Äô, 22‚Äô) and Korou Singh‚Äôs acrobatic strike (34‚Äô) sealed a comfortable victory for the Blasters, who now sit top of the group with six points from two matches. The result also confirmed SC Delhi‚Äôs elimination from the tournament, while Kerala Blasters strengthened their bid for a semi-final berth.

Chandra Brar presents ‚ÄòDriver Mehkma‚Äô ‚Äì love on the highway of life

Song- Driver Mehkma
Singer- Chandra Brar feat Gurlez Akhtar 
Female Lead- Prabh Grewal
Lyrics & Composer- Chandra Brar
Music- Gaiphy
DOP- Prabh Ramgarhia
DOP Asst.- Ajay Sartan
Making- Jagjeet
Edit- Krypton
CC- Fateh Sidhu
Female Costumes- Label Parul Prabhakar
Makeup-Ravi (Makeup Killer)
Bhangra- Damandeep
Directed by The Mohit Bawa

Directions Team - Ritik Kataria, Bhavik Khurrana, Maan Singh
Line Producer- Amandeep Singh, Davinder Singh
Co Artists- Gurshaan, Tari Baba , jeevan john , tejpal
Project by- Adab Entertainment, Karanvirr
Online Promotion- Vibeline Media
Special Thanks - Mela Brar Sarpanch & Baghapurana Truck Union
Produced by- Buta Brar

Song Lyrics:
Boy- Tu bas mere nede tede reha kar ni, Main kehda amrish puri aan jo dardi
Girl- Kitho Card laun walya Afford krli, Mai rann c pyor heroine vrgi
B-Oxygen lagge tu menu saah vargi, Teri lod ae driver nu chaa vargi-2
 Ni tu jande America sohne raah vargi

G-Ena bolda ae tadke jo khawe adya, Gaddi chad k tu fone v na lawe adya
B-Tu jdo di hye zindgi ch aa gyi, Odan da vehde saade chann chadya
G- mude hafta na bhull jawe raah sohnya, 
Tere lad lag rhi aan pachta sohnya-2
Jawe mehkme ch koi na viah sohneya
Tere lad lag rhi a pashtaa sohneya

G-ve ghar vich rakhe bas kaid krk
     Supne dikhonda c lijau chann te
B- ni tenu v dwadu jhoota lame root da, Behja tu connector nal ban k
tu menu mili nek g slaah vrgi
Teri lod ae driver.....

B-Ho laadan nal rakhi kude tere wangra
Tahio jatt chad da jutti nu jhaad k
G-Ve sandle mere lai tethon judde nhio, Saunkan meri de nwe tair chaad te
Mainu gussa kyo chdauna bewjaah sohneya
Tere lad lag rhi.....

B- O dukh tod dinni ae tu kol beh ke
G- Jee laa tan laina ae door reh ke
B- Jhootha smjhi na jatt de pyar nu
G- Jawen kaandle tu bikaner keh ke
B- Ni muhro bolda ni gussa tera seh ke
B- Ni tere taahne jande kaalje nu kheh ke
G-Rose mere lyi lyaya kde dass khan
Tu aawe post de full nitt lai ke
G- Ve rakhen Chandreya mixy ch pa sohneya
 Tere lad lag rhi a pashtaa sohneya
B- Teri lod a driver nu chah vrgi
G- Tere lad lag rhi a pachta sohneya
B- ni tu Bikaner jande sohne raah vargi
G- Jawe mehkme ch koi na viah sohneya
B- Ni tu jande kashmir sohne raah vrgi
G- Tere lad lag rahi aan pachta sohnya
B- ni tu MP nu jande sohne raah vargi
G- jwe mehkme ch koi na vyah sohnya
B- teri mehak ae pahadan di hawa vargi
G- tere lad lad lag rahi aan pachta sohnya
B- ni tu jande Amrica sohne raah vargi
G- jwe mehkme ch koi na vyah sohnya
B- teri lod ae Driver nu chaah vargi
#Drivermehkma #chandrabrar #newpunjabi song
